CatDescriptText: The late Evangelist Josephine [Wallace] Organ and her sister Margie [Wallace] Garner were members of a popular gospel group calle the Gospel Psalm.  They were the first gospel group to sponsor a cruise on the Gateway Clipper. Three church banners in the left of the image read, "Banner Attendance Class" and "Banner Class Offering".
TitMainTitle: Members of Gospel Alms, Margie Wallace (Garner), Lessa Lucky, Mrs. Connors, Josephine Wallace (Organ) and unknown woman, possibly Wilhelmina Cooper, seated behind them, holding six-packs of Pepsi, Diet Pepsi and Mountain Dew, in church basement
